WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:46.160
The Shogun and the Oiran

3
00:01:47.350 --> 00:01:51.840
Now, I give you one chance
to answer my question.

4
00:01:53.210 --> 00:01:56.510
Who are you and what were you doing here?

5
00:01:58.170 --> 00:02:01.800
If you are honest, I will grant you
an instantaneous, painless death.

6
00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:11.670
If you speak falsely, you will face
torture most merciless...

7
00:02:14.430 --> 00:02:15.610
You know me as...

8
00:02:17.090 --> 00:02:18.700
the Witching Hour Boy.

9
00:02:19.910 --> 00:02:24.740
I was investigating how finances
flow through the Flower Capital.

10
00:02:29.570 --> 00:02:30.790
I see.

11
00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:35.550
So you claim you were doing research
on who your next target should be?

12
00:02:37.270 --> 00:02:39.480
A clever answer...

13
00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:44.310
However, we know you are
not who you say you are!

14
00:03:01.700 --> 00:03:03.610
I won't let you escape!

15
00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:07.790
The way you move confirms that
you are no common geisha.

16
00:03:07.790 --> 00:03:14.100
You told us you are the Witching Hour Boy
to hide your identity and pin this on the thief.

17
00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:15.340
How cold!

18
00:03:15.340 --> 00:03:20.510
Indeed. The Witching Hour Boy
was just spotted in the capital.

19
00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:26.470
Let me ask one more time.

20
00:03:26.850 --> 00:03:31.230
Who are you? What were you doing here?

21
00:03:32.940 --> 00:03:36.390
I had no idea you were
so fond of being tortured.

22
00:03:37.230 --> 00:03:38.730
So be it!

23
00:03:45.330 --> 00:03:46.530
Begin!

24
00:04:06.190 --> 00:04:06.760
What?!

25
00:04:06.760 --> 00:04:08.190
She vanished?!

26
00:04:08.190 --> 00:04:09.770
Where did she go?

27
00:04:12.230 --> 00:04:15.910
That could have been dire
if I hadn't used a clone.

28
00:04:17.430 --> 00:04:18.400
This is Orobi!

29
00:04:19.130 --> 00:04:22.390
Onami! Shinobu! Bonekichi!

30
00:04:23.250 --> 00:04:25.530
I apologize. The enemy discovered me!

31
00:04:25.530 --> 00:04:26.290
– What?
– What?

32
00:04:26.290 --> 00:04:27.830
They found Robin?

33
00:04:27.830 --> 00:04:30.540
Oh no! This is a big problem!

34
00:04:30.930 --> 00:04:33.410
It's hard to believe they would find Orobi!

35
00:04:33.410 --> 00:04:38.340
There are ninja in the castle!
At least eleven by my count!

36
00:04:38.340 --> 00:04:40.250
Eleven ninja?!

37
00:04:41.330 --> 00:04:43.090
Fukurokuju!

38
00:04:43.090 --> 00:04:46.230
Fukurokuju is the leader of a ninja unit.

39
00:04:46.790 --> 00:04:51.010
They are the Orochi
Oniwabanshu, an elite force!

40
00:04:52.030 --> 00:04:56.190
I'm sure they'll go after Orobi!
Let's protect her, Onami!

41
00:04:56.590 --> 00:04:59.690
Okay! Robin, where are you?!

42
00:04:59.690 --> 00:05:02.490
Hey! You're a geisha, right?

43
00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.360
Oh, yes!

44
00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:06.860
What're you doing out here? Oops...

45
00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:09.390
Easy there. Please watch your step.

46
00:05:10.390 --> 00:05:12.410
I got so drunk...

47
00:05:12.410 --> 00:05:14.990
I gotta go to the bathroom...

48
00:05:14.990 --> 00:05:17.710
I'll take a leak so I can drink some more!

49
00:05:25.710 --> 00:05:26.680
We lost the signal.

50
00:05:27.030 --> 00:05:29.730
We have to find her ourselves.

51
00:05:29.730 --> 00:05:31.350
Brook, did you hear that?

52
00:05:31.670 --> 00:05:33.790
Find and protect Robin.

53
00:05:33.790 --> 00:05:37.030
Okay, okay! I got it.

54
00:05:39.390 --> 00:05:43.860
And here I finally got to do something
other than gathering food...

55
00:05:45.110 --> 00:05:48.860
A curse on you!

56
00:05:50.390 --> 00:05:52.690
Was she a ninja?

57
00:05:52.690 --> 00:05:54.330
Or perhaps a specter?

58
00:05:54.330 --> 00:05:59.380
It doesn't matter if it was ninjutsu or magic,
her real body must be nearby.

59
00:05:59.780 --> 00:06:00.630
Listen up!

60
00:06:01.110 --> 00:06:03.620
Shogun Orochi is holding a banquet!

61
00:06:03.620 --> 00:06:08.050
Let's not raise a ruckus over one measly rat!

62
00:06:08.050 --> 00:06:09.110
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

63
00:06:15.640 --> 00:06:19.030
Now, let's drink some more...!

64
00:06:19.030 --> 00:06:21.230
Oh, no, you mustn't overdo it.

65
00:06:22.970 --> 00:06:26.290
Oh, how lovely!

66
00:06:28.650 --> 00:06:32.930
Oh, it's the new girl Orobi!
Where have you been?!

67
00:06:32.930 --> 00:06:33.740
Come over here!

68
00:06:33.740 --> 00:06:35.410
Yes, my lord!

69
00:06:36.830 --> 00:06:39.250
"A wise man hides a leaf in the forest."

70
00:06:39.250 --> 00:06:44.710
Escape is no longer an option,
but I still have tasks to carry out.

71
00:06:46.830 --> 00:06:47.970
I'm sorry...

72
00:06:47.970 --> 00:06:49.810
I took so long...

73
00:06:50.370 --> 00:06:51.340
my lord!

74
00:06:57.510 --> 00:07:02.060
Even if I get bone-tired—because I'm
all bones—I'll keep looking for her.

75
00:07:03.730 --> 00:07:05.400
Is she here?

76
00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:08.440
Or here?

77
00:07:11.410 --> 00:07:13.160
Ah! Crud!

78
00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:14.320
Who are you?!

79
00:07:14.320 --> 00:07:15.160
Halt!

80
00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:17.330
What are you doing over there?!

81
00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.000
Oh?

82
00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.040
Where did they go?!

83
00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:27.300
You saw me!

84
00:07:29.550 --> 00:07:31.690
S-S-Something's here!

85
00:07:31.690 --> 00:07:33.510
It's a specter!

86
00:07:37.330 --> 00:07:41.940
Wow! So, all those wonderful treasures
will be taken to Onigashima?

87
00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:46.480
That's right!

88
00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:50.950
Do you want to hear more about
the Fire Festival, Orobi?

89
00:07:50.950 --> 00:07:56.090
Oh, yes, I want to hear
so much more about you.

90
00:07:56.090 --> 00:08:01.010
In that case, how would you like to be
in the running to become my primary consort?

91
00:08:07.170 --> 00:08:08.740
Komurasaki!

92
00:08:08.740 --> 00:08:11.220
My lord plays with my heart...

93
00:08:13.430 --> 00:08:17.230
Don't pout, don't pout, Komurasaki!

94
00:08:17.230 --> 00:08:19.560
My cute, darling dearest!

95
00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:21.140
Is Shogun Orochi...

96
00:08:21.610 --> 00:08:24.650
aware that there is another side to her?

97
00:08:25.350 --> 00:08:30.330
Even if he knew, he would
overlook it because of her beauty.

98
00:08:30.330 --> 00:08:32.770
How adorable!

99
00:08:34.850 --> 00:08:37.970
Hm? Is something wrong, Orobi?

100
00:08:37.970 --> 00:08:39.080
Oh, it's nothing...

101
00:08:47.420 --> 00:08:49.430
Here you go, my Lord!

102
00:08:52.750 --> 00:08:56.800
Sake really hits the spot when
Komurasaki serves it!

103
00:08:58.850 --> 00:09:02.610
Our top oiran Komuraski... What a beauty!

104
00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:05.100
I wish I were Shogun Orochi...

105
00:09:05.100 --> 00:09:08.810
but that darker side of hers truly frightens me!

106
00:09:10.090 --> 00:09:13.390
Forget about it! She'd never
go for you anyway!

107
00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:14.290
Right?!

108
00:09:14.290 --> 00:09:19.700
She's had more training than any of
the other women from your pleasure hall,

109
00:09:19.700 --> 00:09:21.790
Boss Kyoshiro.

110
00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:25.870
You shouldn't confuse
a courtesan with a pet dog.

111
00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:27.630
People are flowers.

112
00:09:27.630 --> 00:09:32.710
Unless you are clean water,
a lady will not bloom elegantly.

113
00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:35.330
You got us there!

114
00:09:35.330 --> 00:09:40.300
But I heard you sent the Soaring Six
just to take down a soba cook!

115
00:09:40.300 --> 00:09:42.180
You're as merciless as ever!

116
00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:48.230
We yakuza become parents to our
underlings once we exchange cups of sake.

117
00:09:49.210 --> 00:09:54.990
If your kid came home beaten up,
what would you do?

118
00:09:54.990 --> 00:09:57.970
I've always been in awe of
your chivalrous spirit.

119
00:09:57.970 --> 00:10:00.870
You're absolutely right, Kyoshiro!

120
00:10:02.870 --> 00:10:07.080
You must always crush your enemy
with overwhelming force!

121
00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:10.500
It ensures that they never
rise back up against you!

122
00:10:11.190 --> 00:10:12.790
Even if they happen to be...

123
00:10:14.300 --> 00:10:17.130
ghosts!

124
00:10:21.470 --> 00:10:24.680
Your lackeys getting beaten
is just the tip of the iceberg.

125
00:10:24.680 --> 00:10:26.450
Kyoshiro.

126
00:10:29.850 --> 00:10:33.520
Outsiders are infiltrating the capital!

127
00:10:35.670 --> 00:10:40.020
Listen, up! Since I have you
all here, I'll say it once more!

128
00:10:40.510 --> 00:10:45.120
Twenty years have passed
since the death of Kozuki Oden!

129
00:10:45.490 --> 00:10:49.290
His wife Toki said that this would
be the year of their vengeance!

130
00:10:49.710 --> 00:10:53.450
Oden's legacy persists!

131
00:10:59.220 --> 00:11:01.470
It's that old ghost story again...

132
00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:04.510
Who even remembers the Kozuki anymore...?

133
00:11:04.510 --> 00:11:06.690
Don't you agree, Komurasaki?

134
00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:13.690
Remember how formidable
Oden's Nine Red Scabbards were?!

135
00:11:13.690 --> 00:11:18.150
Their leader, Kin'emon,
is exceptionally cunning!

136
00:11:18.150 --> 00:11:24.370
Twenty years later, they have returned
to Wano and are conspiring their plot!

137
00:11:29.130 --> 00:11:30.910
They will come...

138
00:11:38.420 --> 00:11:41.930
to take my head!

139
00:11:46.530 --> 00:11:51.800
We've already buried a good deal
of people related to Oden...

140
00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:54.630
but he's still afraid of the Kozuki Clan?

141
00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:01.080
Even though Kaido just
took down one of our enemies,

142
00:12:01.080 --> 00:12:05.370
it wasn't before a yokozuna and some of
Jack's men were attacked in Kuri!

143
00:12:05.730 --> 00:12:11.170
There's the soba cook from the capital and the ronin
from the post town who both attacked our yakuza!

144
00:12:17.410 --> 00:12:20.950
It could've all been done on Kin'emon's orders!

145
00:12:27.010 --> 00:12:31.730
Foxfire Kin'emon and the Red Scabbards...

146
00:12:33.130 --> 00:12:36.190
I cannot wait to face them!

147
00:12:36.190 --> 00:12:40.030
I will cut them down with a single stroke!

148
00:12:45.490 --> 00:12:48.200
How dependable you are, Kyoshiro!

149
00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:51.950
Oden died right before my eyes!

150
00:12:52.300 --> 00:12:56.540
But his son Momonosuke is still alive!

151
00:12:58.370 --> 00:13:01.450
That brat's body wasn't found with the rest!

152
00:13:01.450 --> 00:13:05.470
The Kozuki line lives on!

153
00:13:05.470 --> 00:13:09.620
Their goal is no less than
the restoration of the Kozuki Clan...

154
00:13:10.260 --> 00:13:14.680
Of course, they'll attempt
to behead Kaido, too.

155
00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:17.770
They will definitely come!

156
00:13:24.380 --> 00:13:27.320
No one could chop off Kaido's head!

157
00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:30.550
Can he be any more cowardly?!

158
00:13:30.550 --> 00:13:32.330
You're drinking too much!

159
00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:36.250
It'll be your head if he hears you!

160
00:13:36.250 --> 00:13:38.220
Otoko, take this one next!

161
00:13:38.220 --> 00:13:39.250
Okay!

162
00:13:39.250 --> 00:13:41.220
Hey, I'm out of sake!

163
00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:43.110
Yes, we'll be right with you!

164
00:13:43.110 --> 00:13:44.850
Can you take it to him?!

165
00:13:44.850 --> 00:13:45.880
Yes, ma'am!

166
00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:49.760
I'm telling you, this is the year!

167
00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:53.230
Remember Toki's last words!

168
00:13:53.230 --> 00:13:56.250
Be on your guard!

169
00:13:56.250 --> 00:13:57.600
He's so paranoid.

170
00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:59.190
It's pathetic.

171
00:13:59.190 --> 00:14:02.360
When will he realize that poem
is pure nonsense?

172
00:14:03.170 --> 00:14:06.650
"You are the moon, unaware
of the approach of daybreak."

173
00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:11.780
Here we go again... Now the sake is ruined.

174
00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:15.500
"May your purpose be fulfilled...

175
00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:20.500
and cast nine shadows on
the night woven of twenty years.

176
00:14:20.830 --> 00:14:25.010
Then you shall know the brilliance of dawn!"

177
00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:27.590
The meaning is clear!

178
00:14:27.590 --> 00:14:30.950
After twenty years, on a moonlit night,

179
00:14:30.950 --> 00:14:34.510
the ghosts of those nine samurai will come...

180
00:14:36.270 --> 00:14:40.070
and enact their vengeance by killing me...

181
00:14:40.620 --> 00:14:43.820
and in doing so open Wano!

182
00:14:54.130 --> 00:14:57.750
Orochi is very set in his
belief of the prophecy...

183
00:14:58.430 --> 00:15:01.250
But his subordinates don't
seem to take it seriously.

184
00:15:02.130 --> 00:15:03.420
That's not surprising.

185
00:15:05.550 --> 00:15:07.130
He's so delusional...

186
00:15:07.580 --> 00:15:11.130
Oden and the Red Scabbards are all dead!

187
00:15:11.130 --> 00:15:13.010
They're not even a memory for me.

188
00:15:13.600 --> 00:15:15.560
What a coward.

189
00:15:16.160 --> 00:15:19.640
We won't allow them to come
and do as they please!

190
00:15:23.770 --> 00:15:28.470
We cannot afford to lower our guard...

191
00:15:35.410 --> 00:15:37.160
Who's doing that? Cut it out, idiot!

192
00:15:39.950 --> 00:15:42.620
You can't laugh! Hold it in!

193
00:15:47.350 --> 00:15:49.110
Who was that?!

194
00:15:50.490 --> 00:15:53.650
Did someone actually laugh at me?!

195
00:15:56.180 --> 00:15:57.470
Otoko!

196
00:15:57.470 --> 00:16:02.030
Everyone thinks he's a fool!

197
00:16:03.390 --> 00:16:06.110
Cut it out! Just leave already!

198
00:16:09.250 --> 00:16:13.600
I can't stop! I'm so sorry!

199
00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:15.820
– It's a child!
– She's the oiran's attendant!

200
00:16:16.320 --> 00:16:17.620
Stop her!

201
00:16:17.930 --> 00:16:19.080
Otoko!

202
00:16:20.450 --> 00:16:22.850
I know I shouldn't laugh!

203
00:16:30.370 --> 00:16:32.220
How distasteful!

204
00:16:32.690 --> 00:16:35.640
I am the shogun!

205
00:16:42.990 --> 00:16:44.480
Stop her!

206
00:16:48.970 --> 00:16:52.410
A twenty-year-old grudge...

207
00:16:53.490 --> 00:16:56.070
Do you actually think...?

208
00:16:57.010 --> 00:17:01.250
Do you think it frightens me?!

209
00:17:03.830 --> 00:17:06.460
I am the victor!

210
00:17:08.430 --> 00:17:09.460
My lord!

211
00:17:09.460 --> 00:17:11.760
I defeated Oden!

212
00:17:12.180 --> 00:17:13.880
Please! Stop it!

213
00:17:18.890 --> 00:17:20.260
Stop this!

214
00:17:21.910 --> 00:17:23.200
The oiran!

215
00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.600
It's useless!

216
00:17:24.600 --> 00:17:27.560
That black-hearted woman can't do anything!

217
00:17:28.030 --> 00:17:28.810
My lord!

218
00:17:30.350 --> 00:17:32.110
She is but a child.

219
00:17:32.110 --> 00:17:34.820
Stay out of this, Komurasaki!

220
00:17:44.570 --> 00:17:46.540
My lord, please forgive her!

221
00:17:47.490 --> 00:17:49.710
You dare laugh at me?!

222
00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:52.690
You whelp!

223
00:17:59.330 --> 00:18:03.090
She's prone to laughter!
She means no offense!

224
00:18:03.090 --> 00:18:06.890
There's no stopping him now!
Forget about her!

225
00:18:06.890 --> 00:18:10.770
My lord! She's just a child! Have mercy!

226
00:18:10.770 --> 00:18:13.910
Listen to me when I speak!

227
00:18:14.710 --> 00:18:15.990
Stop laughing!

228
00:18:19.730 --> 00:18:21.110
Otoko!

229
00:18:52.670 --> 00:18:54.690
Komurasaki...

230
00:18:55.170 --> 00:18:57.150
Why...?

231
00:18:57.150 --> 00:18:59.950
How could you strike me?

232
00:18:59.950 --> 00:19:02.280
Apologize, Komurasaki!

233
00:19:02.690 --> 00:19:06.520
Bow until your forehead sinks into the floor!

234
00:19:06.520 --> 00:19:08.080
I refuse!

235
00:19:13.380 --> 00:19:17.840
I will never abase myself before anyone!

236
00:19:19.630 --> 00:19:21.340
How dare she!

237
00:19:21.340 --> 00:19:26.310
When I know I am right,
I have no need to even give an inch!

238
00:19:27.630 --> 00:19:30.410
Hey, Komurasaki...

239
00:19:31.570 --> 00:19:33.020
I was going to make you...

240
00:19:34.270 --> 00:19:39.530
the wife of the shogun.

241
00:19:39.860 --> 00:19:42.410
If you would prefer a weak woman...

242
00:19:42.890 --> 00:19:46.110
then please, take your blade to my flesh!

243
00:19:48.870 --> 00:19:50.750
I am the daughter of a samurai!

244
00:19:50.750 --> 00:19:52.310
Silence!

245
00:19:52.830 --> 00:19:55.710
I will not live in disgrace!

246
00:19:59.330 --> 00:20:02.380
How impertinent...!

247
00:20:07.770 --> 00:20:12.350
You're nothing more than a whore!

248
00:20:18.570 --> 00:20:23.070
Don't act like you know a damn thing
about the ways of the samurai!

249
00:20:32.890 --> 00:20:34.710
Shogun Orochi...?!

250
00:20:37.930 --> 00:20:39.420
He transformed.

251
00:20:41.340 --> 00:20:44.470
Komurasaki...

252
00:20:45.560 --> 00:20:50.010
Mythical Snake Snake Fruit:
Yamata no Orochi

253
00:20:55.350 --> 00:20:57.490
What a waste...

254
00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:01.390
It'd be a shame to lose such beauty!

255
00:21:01.390 --> 00:21:05.270
I'd rather not chew up your head!

256
00:21:06.360 --> 00:21:08.200
Apologize!

257
00:21:08.200 --> 00:21:11.200
If you beg for your life,

258
00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:14.160
you will get a lighter sentence!

259
00:21:19.690 --> 00:21:23.310
What are you waiting for?!

260
00:21:24.990 --> 00:21:28.690
Apologize from the bottom of your heart!

261
00:21:30.430 --> 00:21:33.060
You should learn to let things go...

262
00:21:38.650 --> 00:21:41.440
They say whoever falls in love loses.

263
00:21:42.810 --> 00:21:44.280
What?!

264
00:21:44.610 --> 00:21:46.430
I...

265
00:21:46.430 --> 00:21:48.710
will not beg for my life!

266
00:21:51.790 --> 00:21:54.290
She's provoking him...

267
00:21:54.290 --> 00:21:56.870
Stop it, Komurasaki!

268
00:21:56.870 --> 00:22:01.420
Komurasaki!

269
00:22:08.970 --> 00:22:12.310
Damn you!

270
00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:25.280
Shogun Orochi, why are you attacking us?!

271
00:22:27.630 --> 00:22:31.280
How insolent!

272
00:22:44.330 --> 00:22:47.970
Huh? Aren't you the lady
from the soba shop?!

273
00:22:47.970 --> 00:22:50.930
Otoko! I'm glad you're okay.

274
00:22:50.930 --> 00:22:55.590
Where did that sorceress go?!

275
00:22:58.980 --> 00:23:00.810
Hold it right there!

276
00:23:01.270 --> 00:23:04.610
You thought you could deceive us?!

277
00:23:04.610 --> 00:23:06.940
I found the woman!

278
00:23:11.950 --> 00:23:14.330
Very well, Komurasaki!

279
00:23:15.190 --> 00:23:17.330
As you wish,

280
00:23:17.330 --> 00:23:20.460
I will kill you with my own hands!

281
00:23:50.950 --> 00:23:53.890
Verily, this is pandemonium!

282
00:24:07.920 --> 00:24:10.170
Prepare yourself!

283
00:24:13.720 --> 00:24:16.510
Komurasaki!

284
00:24:18.230 --> 00:24:19.060
Daikoku!

285
00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:22.730
Why aren't you ninja stopping the shogun?!

286
00:24:23.060 --> 00:24:24.750
Save the oiran!

287
00:24:24.750 --> 00:24:28.650
He's free to do what he wants.
Nothing can stop him.

288
00:24:30.400 --> 00:24:32.360
More importantly,

289
00:24:32.360 --> 00:24:36.570
we're currently dealing with an intruder!

290
00:24:36.570 --> 00:24:38.210
An intruder?!

291
00:24:48.170 --> 00:24:51.400
Orobi is an intruder?

292
00:24:51.400 --> 00:24:55.340
Come to think of it, I've never
seen her before now!

293
00:25:00.050 --> 00:25:03.430
Hey, lady, please save the oiran.

294
00:25:03.910 --> 00:25:05.690
I can't!

295
00:25:05.690 --> 00:25:10.070
I don't even know if I can save you
after the way you angered the shogun!

296
00:25:26.580 --> 00:25:28.500
Help us!

297
00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:32.460
It's a curse of death!

298
00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:34.800
What's going on over there?!

299
00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:40.140
Fujin! Raijin! What's going on?!

300
00:25:48.330 --> 00:25:50.650
I-It's a specter!

301
00:25:50.650 --> 00:25:54.610
The gashadokuro yokai really exists!

302
00:25:55.780 --> 00:26:02.370
A curse on you!

303
00:26:02.370 --> 00:26:03.950
What?!

304
00:26:05.960 --> 00:26:07.830
A ghost!

305
00:26:09.290 --> 00:26:10.290
Otoko!

306
00:26:10.290 --> 00:26:15.130
A curse on you!

307
00:26:17.510 --> 00:26:19.410
Robin, I'm glad you're all right!

308
00:26:19.410 --> 00:26:21.680
Bonekichi, you're a hero! Thanks!

309
00:26:23.830 --> 00:26:25.640
I'm awesome, am I?

310
00:26:26.030 --> 00:26:27.730
Keep it up!

311
00:26:27.730 --> 00:26:30.520
Let's get out of here!

312
00:26:31.870 --> 00:26:35.650
Are they allied with the specter?!

313
00:26:35.650 --> 00:26:36.820
Mil Fleurs!

314
00:26:38.790 --> 00:26:40.770
Gigantesco Mano!

315
00:26:47.160 --> 00:26:48.650
How could you...?!

316
00:26:48.650 --> 00:26:49.420
Damn you!

317
00:26:54.030 --> 00:26:54.880
I have her!

318
00:26:57.610 --> 00:26:59.630
Th-The gashadokuro!

319
00:26:59.630 --> 00:27:02.720
Allow me to guide you to the land of the dead,

320
00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:05.750
young lady!

321
00:27:09.970 --> 00:27:11.230
Go away!

322
00:27:11.230 --> 00:27:12.860
– No!
– No!

323
00:27:19.860 --> 00:27:22.530
It's both Robin and Brook...

324
00:27:22.530 --> 00:27:24.200
What should we do?!

325
00:27:24.200 --> 00:27:26.370
There's no point in staying hidden.

326
00:27:26.370 --> 00:27:30.330
The Castle Attic

327
00:27:26.920 --> 00:27:28.750
Let's go!

328
00:27:28.750 --> 00:27:30.330
Understood, Shinobu!

329
00:27:34.610 --> 00:27:36.500
Who's there?! A ninja?!

330
00:27:40.370 --> 00:27:45.410
Hey, miss! She just called you
"Shinobu," didn't she?!

331
00:27:45.410 --> 00:27:47.260
Is that you...

332
00:27:47.260 --> 00:27:48.180
Hanzo?!

333
00:27:49.730 --> 00:27:53.150
So you're alive! The man-seducing...

334
00:27:53.490 --> 00:27:55.360
sexy kunoichi.

335
00:28:09.050 --> 00:28:11.250
Shinobu the Man-Killer!

336
00:28:23.890 --> 00:28:25.840
How did you know?

337
00:28:25.840 --> 00:28:27.100
No, you're not her.

338
00:28:27.720 --> 00:28:29.140
Forget it!

339
00:28:29.140 --> 00:28:30.930
It is me!

340
00:28:33.100 --> 00:28:35.990
Ninpo: Ballbuster!

341
00:28:35.990 --> 00:28:37.400
That was ninjutsu?!

342
00:28:40.050 --> 00:28:45.150
This is why... you're
known as... the Man-Killer.

343
00:28:45.150 --> 00:28:46.990
That's why?!

344
00:28:46.990 --> 00:28:49.410
I-I can't move...

345
00:28:49.410 --> 00:28:52.250
Ninpo: Paralysis Technique!

346
00:28:52.250 --> 00:28:54.420
What?! You just made that up!

347
00:28:54.820 --> 00:28:56.320
We have to get going!

348
00:28:56.320 --> 00:28:57.540
Let's go, Onami!

349
00:28:57.550 --> 00:28:58.040
What?

350
00:28:59.230 --> 00:29:00.630
Sexy Ninpo:

351
00:29:00.970 --> 00:29:02.630
Rot Garden!

352
00:29:19.940 --> 00:29:22.520
Why did Hanzo fall down from the attic?

353
00:29:22.520 --> 00:29:25.320
Who are those two kunoichi?!

354
00:29:25.320 --> 00:29:27.150
What's going on?!

355
00:29:27.150 --> 00:29:29.120
The banquet room is a mess!

356
00:29:45.190 --> 00:29:46.970
Whoa, Onami!

357
00:29:47.630 --> 00:29:50.890
A curse on you!

358
00:29:52.210 --> 00:29:52.970
Why on me?!

359
00:29:53.580 --> 00:29:54.350
Onami!

360
00:29:54.760 --> 00:29:56.020
I'm here to help!

361
00:29:59.590 --> 00:30:03.430
Where are you, Komurasaki?!

362
00:30:04.490 --> 00:30:06.200
There you are!

363
00:30:21.910 --> 00:30:23.710
Kyoshiro?!

364
00:30:44.970 --> 00:30:48.270
You should not have done that, Komurasaki...

365
00:30:52.210 --> 00:30:53.710
Are you prepared?

366
00:30:53.710 --> 00:30:54.830
I am.

367
00:32:14.490 --> 00:32:17.280
The... The oiran...!

368
00:32:18.770 --> 00:32:19.830
Big Sis...!

369
00:32:25.540 --> 00:32:30.130
Boss Kyoshiro, why did you do that?

370
00:32:30.130 --> 00:32:33.260
She was the most beautiful woman in Wano...!

371
00:32:33.260 --> 00:32:34.760
This is heartrending!

372
00:32:48.390 --> 00:32:50.530
Komurasaki...

373
00:32:57.110 --> 00:32:59.410
What have you done, Kyoshiro?!

374
00:33:01.730 --> 00:33:04.710
Did I tell you to kill her?!

375
00:33:05.730 --> 00:33:09.290
You upstart...!

376
00:33:12.970 --> 00:33:14.470
This was...

377
00:33:15.720 --> 00:33:19.510
a samurai's act of mercy for Komurasaki.

378
00:33:20.310 --> 00:33:24.730
Defying the shogun is a grave crime,
regardless of one's status!

379
00:33:25.910 --> 00:33:28.440
That law is ironclad.

380
00:33:30.320 --> 00:33:33.490
He did it as a show of loyalty?!

381
00:33:33.490 --> 00:33:36.530
Kyoshiro has gone too far...

382
00:33:57.380 --> 00:33:59.470
Give me...

383
00:34:01.560 --> 00:34:03.890
that whelp!

384
00:34:06.810 --> 00:34:09.980
I will chew her to death!

385
00:34:13.820 --> 00:34:20.030
If you hadn't laughed at me,
she wouldn't have had to die!

386
00:34:20.030 --> 00:34:21.370
You brat!

387
00:34:23.330 --> 00:34:25.290
Hand her over, Orobi!

388
00:34:25.290 --> 00:34:28.170
Who the hell are you anyway?!

389
00:34:31.420 --> 00:34:32.340
Robin!

390
00:34:32.340 --> 00:34:34.090
Get out here, Zeus!

391
00:34:35.920 --> 00:34:39.800
Hey! Did you call for me, Nami?

392
00:34:39.800 --> 00:34:42.100
I want to give you some weather eggs.

393
00:34:42.100 --> 00:34:43.390
Yeah?!

394
00:34:47.230 --> 00:34:49.190
A curse on you...

395
00:34:49.190 --> 00:34:52.170
This is no time for us
to be chased by a ghost!

396
00:34:52.170 --> 00:34:54.150
A curse on you...

397
00:34:54.150 --> 00:34:56.550
Why isn't it attacking?!

398
00:34:56.550 --> 00:34:59.570
A curse on you!

399
00:35:01.240 --> 00:35:02.910
Oh, dear! They noticed!

400
00:35:02.910 --> 00:35:05.410
Guess it's time to go.

401
00:35:06.910 --> 00:35:09.520
It's time to fight!

402
00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:11.830
There is trouble in the banquet hall!

403
00:35:12.240 --> 00:35:15.550
Capture the intruders and exorcise the yokai!

404
00:35:19.680 --> 00:35:22.850
Contain Shogun Orochi's rampage!

405
00:35:33.150 --> 00:35:35.270
Everyone, hit the deck!

406
00:35:35.270 --> 00:35:36.650
Ninpo:

407
00:35:37.230 --> 00:35:38.570
Thunderbolt!

408
00:35:44.990 --> 00:35:47.450
What the hell?!

409
00:36:02.030 --> 00:36:05.050
You're young, but that was
one impressive ninpo!

410
00:36:05.050 --> 00:36:06.720
That was close!

411
00:36:06.720 --> 00:36:08.850
Only you could've pulled it off, Onami!

412
00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:24.110
The Next Morning
Okobore Town
Kuri, Wano
Nine Days Until
the Final Battle

413
00:36:21.880 --> 00:36:24.110
Have some oshiruko. Go ahead, Olin, try it!

414
00:36:27.990 --> 00:36:30.830
Wow! It smells delicious!

415
00:36:30.830 --> 00:36:32.750
Thank you!

416
00:36:35.880 --> 00:36:37.340
So good!

417
00:36:37.670 --> 00:36:39.760
It's yummy!

418
00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:43.590
This red bean soup is so sweet and tasty!

419
00:36:43.590 --> 00:36:46.220
I'm glad that you like it.

420
00:36:48.830 --> 00:36:51.850
I'm sorry, Olin, but that's all we had.

421
00:36:51.850 --> 00:36:54.450
I wish I could have more.

422
00:36:54.450 --> 00:36:58.690
But you fed me even though you barely
have anything. Thank you, Miss Tsuru.

423
00:37:02.070 --> 00:37:05.410
Is she really that strong?

424
00:37:05.410 --> 00:37:07.930
Yeah, stronger than you'll ever know...

425
00:37:07.930 --> 00:37:12.370
Then let's get her to rescue Big Bro
from the prison in Udon!

426
00:37:12.370 --> 00:37:13.680
What?!

427
00:37:13.680 --> 00:37:15.750
Oh, that's a great idea!

428
00:37:15.750 --> 00:37:17.840
It's not that easy!

429
00:37:17.840 --> 00:37:21.090
She'll never listen to us!

430
00:37:21.090 --> 00:37:23.770
Let's do this, Chopperemon!

431
00:37:23.770 --> 00:37:25.010
Let's go!

432
00:37:32.390 --> 00:37:36.730
Are you sure? If she gets her
memory back, we're done for!

433
00:37:36.730 --> 00:37:39.450
It's better than just waiting here!

434
00:37:39.450 --> 00:37:41.860
I want to go! This is our chance!

435
00:37:49.190 --> 00:37:50.410
Um...

436
00:37:50.410 --> 00:37:54.210
What is it, cute little Chopperemon?

437
00:37:54.210 --> 00:37:54.960
Put 'er there.

438
00:37:57.430 --> 00:37:59.420
O-Okay...

439
00:38:02.070 --> 00:38:04.010
I'm hungry...

440
00:38:05.270 --> 00:38:07.880
I wanna eat more...

441
00:38:07.930 --> 00:38:10.280
I'm seriously scared!

442
00:38:10.780 --> 00:38:12.990
We need your help. Olin.

443
00:38:12.990 --> 00:38:14.030
What?!

444
00:38:14.030 --> 00:38:16.460
Let's go to Udon together!

445
00:38:16.460 --> 00:38:17.600
What?!

446
00:38:17.600 --> 00:38:21.690
Udon? That's where I'm going?

447
00:38:21.690 --> 00:38:23.400
Indeed!

448
00:38:23.400 --> 00:38:28.700
I heard the Superstar in charge
of Udon loves oshiruko!

449
00:38:30.590 --> 00:38:34.200
Yeah, that's right! They have
tons of red-bean soup there!

450
00:38:36.610 --> 00:38:39.500
That lie just slipped out...

451
00:38:39.500 --> 00:38:41.970
If there's no oshiruko there,

452
00:38:41.970 --> 00:38:45.340
she'll kill me!

453
00:38:45.800 --> 00:38:49.670
There's tons of red-bean soup there?!

454
00:38:53.830 --> 00:38:55.060
Then let's get a move on!
